      "content": "but i can see it in their eyes. they're always so tense around me. i feel like if i was just... gone, they could finally breathe. they could have a life that isn't weighed down by my constant struggle. it feels like the only truly selfless thing i could ever do for them is to stop being a problem in their lives. wouldn't that be the kindest way to let them move on?",
